              "help": {
                "text": "Vulnerability CVE-2018-20796\nSeverity: low\nPackage: libc-bin\nVersion: 2.42-14\nFix Version: \nType: deb\nLocation: /var/lib/dpkg/status\nData Namespace: debian:distro:debian:unstable\nLink: [CVE-2018-20796](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2018-20796)",
                "markdown": "**Vulnerability CVE-2018-20796**\n| Severity | Package | Version | Fix Version | Type | Location | Data Namespace | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| low  | libc-bin  | 2.42-14  |   | deb  | /var/lib/dpkg/status  | debian:distro:debian:unstable  | [CVE-2018-20796](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2018-20796)  |\n"
